import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react'; import axios from 'axios'; export const AnalysisTab = () => { const [data, setData] = useState({ costPerUnit: 0, marketRevenue: 0, expenses: 0, dailyVisits: 0, costPerUnitChange: 0, marketRevenueChange: 0, expensesChange: 0, dailyVisitsChange: 0, }); useEffect(() => { const fetchData = async () => { try { const response = await axios.get('http://localhost:5000/api/ev-analysis'); setData(response.data); } catch (error) { console.error('Error fetching data', error); } }; fetchData(); }, []); return (
Daily
Cost per Unit

${data.costPerUnit}

{data.costPerUnitChange}% 0 ? 'mdi-arrow-up text-success' : 'mdi-arrow-down text-danger'}`} />
Per Week
Market Revenue

${data.marketRevenue}

{data.marketRevenueChange}% 0 ? 'mdi-arrow-up text-success' : 'mdi-arrow-down text-danger'}`} />
Per Month
Expenses

${data.expenses}

{data.expensesChange}% 0 ? 'mdi-arrow-up text-success' : 'mdi-arrow-down text-danger'}`} />
All Time
Daily Visits

{data.dailyVisits}

{data.dailyVisitsChange}% 0 ? 'mdi-arrow-up text-success' : 'mdi-arrow-down text-danger'}`} />
); };
